Hi, my name is Mitzi. I am an attractive, slightly older :) BBW Australian woman who truly has zero inhibitions and I truly do love what I do! I am fun, sexy, intelligent, very down to earth and straightforward and I would love the opportunity to please YOU.

When you arrive at my house I like to spend at least ten minutes or more chatting with you and getting to know you. This is on my time since it is important to me to be able to do this.

I am located in the North Bay about 9 miles west of Santa Rosa on the beautiful Russian River. In calls are preferred and I have a very flexible schedule. I live by myself in a very peaceful and private environment. The best way to reach me is by calling my cell phone: (415) 246-8437
Check out my new website: www.aussiemitzi.com
